### Color
``` lua
local pure_red		= Color.new( 255, 0, 0, 255 )
local pure_green	= Color.new( 0, 255, 0, 255 )
local pure_blue		= Color.new( 0, 0, 255, 255 )
local pure_white	= Color.new( 255, 255, 255, 255 )
```

#### Object Creation
`Color.new( r, g, b, a )`

#### Parameters
**`integer`** `r`<br>
&emsp;_The **red** component of the tint. `[0 ~ 255]`_<br>
**`integer`** `g`<br>
&emsp;_The **green** component of the tint. `[0 ~ 255]`_<br>
**`integer`** `b`<br>
&emsp;_The **blue** component of the tint. `[0 ~ 255]`_<br>
**`integer`** `a`<br>
&emsp;_The **alpha** component of the tint. `[0 ~ 255]`_<br>
